The paper deals with image classification, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of multi-view learning and metric learning techniques also suggests that the paper could belong to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions object detection, which is a sub-topic of multimedia (cs.MM) and image retrieval, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
